    - FBI adopted then abandoned due to S&W 1076 issues and grip size
    - Led directly to .40 S&W development (FBI-spec 10mm in shorter case)
    
    Game Balance (Full-Power Configuration):
    - Damage: 50 (between .40 S&W at 36 and .357 Mag at 56)
    - 2 shots close, 5 at range
    - High recoil penalty balances high damage
    - Best semi-auto stopping power outside of magnums
-->
